data.name: txtWelcomeNote.Text
data.value:
Welcome to AdVenture Calculator.
The 'Calculations' tab allows you to perform a number of calculations: -> Total Earned Profit / second -> Business Purchase Cost -> Waiting Time for a monetary goal -> Money needed for an Angel Investor goal [TO-DO]
However before performing calculations, you need to provide some information:
To calculate the purchase cost, you need to select the Managers that you have bought (from the 'Managers' tab). To calculate profit and waiting time you need to select the correct Business levels, Upgrades and Angel Investors.

This software is provided under GNU General Public License v2, and can be obtained from: https://github.com/TrapperHell/AdVentureCalculator
Notes: -> Since I have stopped playing the game altogether, I do not plan on releasing updates anytime soon... -> The last proper update of the code has been quite some time ago, and the latest additions where hastily made to match the above-mentioned version of the game -> This calculator is only applicable for Earth - however the way it is designed, it should be fairly simple to include Moon (in fact there are already some references ;) ), and *MAYBE* even Mars -> When first created, it was intended as a quick, dirty tool to perform calculations, however by time it has grown quite a bit. Some code is quite messy... -> If you decide to modify the code (e.g. refactor code or improve the UI), I'd appreciate if you drop me a line at trapper-hell@hotmail.com :)
